Package: pleb-client
Version: 0.1.1
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libqt6widgets6, libqt6quick6, libqt6qml6, libqt6network6, libqt6multimedia6, qt6-qpa-plugins, qml6-module-qtquick, qml6-module-qtquick-controls, qml6-module-qtquick-layouts, qml6-module-qtmultimedia
Maintainer: PlebOne <contact@pleb.one>
Description: A native Nostr client for Linux
 Pleb Client is a desktop Nostr client built with Qt/QML for Linux.
 Features include:
  - Following feed, replies, and global timeline
  - Direct messages (NIP-04)
  - Notifications
  - Profile management
  - Zaps via NWC (Nostr Wallet Connect)
Homepage: https://pleb.one
